				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Melee while twisting<a name="17344"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 27 04 4:48 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Hello all, I am a lvl 5 bard trying to figure out how to play this class <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
I have read some of the articles for new players (miabell's thread) and i think i understand how to keep 3 songs going on at the same time.
<br />

<br />
I have a question however, regarding meleeing while twisting... it seems to me as long as I am casting a song, i dont melee. So while twisting if i'm casting songs all the time, how can i melee and do damage as well?
<br />

<br />
I have tried waiting a bit more between casts, but that leads to the songs fading.
<br />

<br />
Or is it that the early songs have too little a duration, I shouldnt be trying to melee while twisting until later?
<br />

<br />
thanks for any help<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
