				<td colspan="2"><span>Yeah, once you're up there in levels with skills maxed, and haste in the 115% range, your arms are flailing about madly and it doesn't matter if you're casting/singing or not, you still flail. <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-13.gif" border="0" alt="LOL" hspace="2" />
<br />

<br />
That being said, once in a while on brass songs, I get to swallow my sword while the computer does a horn blowing dance.  I used to think that sucked because I wasn't fighting when that happened, but now I think it's graphical only, and I still melee, just don't see my arms moving. Could be wrong, doesn't really matter because I don't add that much to DPS compared to what my songs do.
<br />

<br />
Hope that helps,
